https://github.com/slara/generator-reveal

1. npm install -g yo
2. npm install -g generator-reveal
    2.1 npm install -g bower
3. yo reveal - in this folder

4. view slides with grunt:
    4.1 npm install -g grunt
    4.2 npm install -g grunt-cli -> for console usage
        grunt serve

5. create slides with:
    yo reveal:slide more-content

